title: Texas staggering after troubling 50-7 loss to No. 4 TCU
text:
> Texas Texas staggering after troubling 50-7 loss to No. 4 TCU Texas head coach Charlie Strong, left, meets with TCU head coach Gary Patterson, right, after TCU defeated Texas 50-7 in an NCAA football game Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Fort Worth, Texas. (AP Photo/Ron Jenkins)
